snippet.title: I Made Minecraft, but It's 4D
snippet.description:
Play the Demo: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1941640/4D_Miner/

Official 4D Miner Discord: https://discord.gg/pMtZa6AVy2
Official Subreddit: https://reddit.com/r/4D_Miner
Official Wiki: https://4d-miner.fandom.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/Mashpoe
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Mashpoe



The Kickstarter campaign has ended and unfortunately was unsuccessful. I am not giving up on this project, and you can still support it through my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Mashpoe

Music in this video:
Roving - Detritus
Rinse Repeat - DivKid
Magenta - Sextile
Cavemen of the Future - Joel Cummins, Andy Farag
Rich in the 80s - DivKid
Digifunk - DivKid
